@lsm5 this is going to need specfile changes:
- easy and recommended IMHO: at install time, `rm .../tutorial.bats`
- hard: build and package the new `tutorial` binary, and make all sorts of changes to gating tests

@nalind do you have any objection to going the easy route? Are the tutorial tests necessary for confidence in Fedora or RHEL environments?
